in every possible way.

00:01:50.700 --> 00:01:53.110
I thought I was going to
write a feature about the war

00:01:53.110 --> 00:01:55.890
on terror set in the
present, and about people

00:01:55.890 --> 00:01:58.360
who are involved in matters
of national security

00:01:58.360 --> 00:02:01.160
