of our political conversation

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:27.530
these days, you find
that all roads lead back

00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:30.024
to the New Mexico
desert and that really

00:02:30.024 --> 00:02:31.440
the story of the
birth of the bomb

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:34.482
is kind of the story of
the birth of 21st century

00:02:34.482 --> 00:02:36.440
America and the world
that we're living in now.

00:02:36.440 --> 00:02:39.860
So I went down a very,
very, very deep rabbit hole,

00:02:39.860 --> 00:02:42.930
