You talked about the changing
television landscape,

00:27:34.210 --> 00:27:36.800
and I feel like
with all the respect

00:27:36.800 --> 00:27:38.300
for a show that's
hyper intelligent,

00:27:38.300 --> 00:27:40.096
and about science,
